column2: SELECT TOP #  s.z as zz, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID WHERE   p.modelMagErr_u BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.modelMagErr_g BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.modelMagErr_r BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.modelMagErr_i BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.modelMagErr_z BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.Class = &&&  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #
